  "instructions": [
    "Chop the onion and bell peppers into thin strips.",
    "Slice the garlic cloves thinly.",
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add chickpeas to the pan and fry until golden brown, about 5 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat and mix with chopped onions, bell peppers, and garlic.",
    "Drizzle hummus on top of the mixture.",
    "Season with salt and pepper as needed. Add mint leaves for a pop of freshness.",
    "Stir in temper sauce to create a creamy consistency.",
    "Serve hot over quinoa or couscous."
